  "prompt": "Where can I buy Soju in mumbai?",
  "response": "Soju, a popular Korean alcoholic beverage, can be purchased in Mumbai at various places, including specialized liquor stores, international grocery stores, and online platforms. Here are some options:\n\n1. **Liquor Stores**:\n   - **Wine & Spirit Shops**: Look for well-stocked wine and spirit shops in areas like Bandra, Colaba, Lower Parel, and Juhu. Some stores may carry imported spirits, including Soju.\n   - **Premium Liquor Stores**: Stores like **Mumbai Wine Club** or **Spencer's Retail** (in select locations) might carry international spirits.\n\n2. **Specialty Stores**:\n   - **Korean or Asian Grocery Stores**: Stores catering to Asian communities often stock Soju. Examples include **Kim\u2019s Mart** or **Asia Mart** in areas like Khar or Sakinaka.\n   - **International Supermarkets**: Stores like **Nature's Basket** or **HyperCITY** sometimes carry imported spirits.\n\n3. **Online Platforms**:\n   - **Liquor Delivery Apps**: Apps like **Living Liquidz**, **Swiggy Wine Shops**, or **The Whisky Shop** often have a wide selection of imported spirits, including Soju.\n   - **E-commerce Websites**: Check platforms like **Amazon** or **BigBasket** for availability.\n\n4. **Korean Restaurants**:\n   - Some Korean restaurants in Mumbai, such as **Ginger Sue** or **Kimaya**, may sell or serve Soju.\n\n*Note*: Availability may vary, and some options may require verification of age and local liquor laws. Always check with the store or website beforehand.",
